LAGOS – The General Overseer of the Sanctuary for the Broken Hearted International Ministries, Prophetess Margaret Ade Mayaki, has called for special prayers for Nigeria, against the enemy’s aggression, wastage of lives due to terrorist’s activities, political unrest, coup detat and invasion. Prophetess Margaret Ade Mayaki in a three batch of prophecies released in the early hours of the New Year will among other goodies be a year of divine fulfilment. “Thus saith the Lord, this year, many will receive their crowns of glory. This year will usher in glorious destinies. It will be a year of divine fulfilment of the lives of believers. The year will usher in floodgates of open heaven to the children of God. Crowns of glory are being released to believers who have done well. Kanu: IPOB, Urges Ndigbo To Storm Umuahia High Court On… Dangote, Emefiele Commend Ogun As Investment-Friendly “This year, heaven is declared open to believers who are working according to My divine will in the name of Jesus Amen. “This year, heaven has released heavenly gifts and royal diadems to worthy children of God. God will multiply our seeds and bring in multiple harvests. The Lord is saying that He is going to cancel the spirit of death that Satan has passed judgment over. Heaven will remove spiritual embargoes placed on the lives of many.